&lt;p>Boards do not need another slide on “what is generative AI.” They need &lt;strong>clear oversight&lt;/strong> of how technology choices create &lt;strong>risk, cost, speed, and reputation&lt;/strong>—and whether management’s plans are &lt;strong>credible, measurable, and governable&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Dr. Hari Thapliyal works with founders, investors, and directors who want a &lt;strong>technology-literate independent voice&lt;/strong> in the room: India-focused and global-facing, from &lt;strong>growth-stage startups&lt;/strong> to &lt;strong>established enterprises&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>